cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.DC 

This paper is related to networking and communication technologies, specifically 5G networks, SDN, and NFV. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a reinforcement learning-based approach, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of QoS and QoE metrics in the proposed approach suggests that it may also be relevant to the categories of systems and control (cs.SY) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with the orchestration of services in dynamic network environments, which could also be relevant to the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
